OL,3,CUniversity tuition fees set to rise by
OL,4,C#285 for first time in eight years
OL,6,FLabour's announcement marks the first
OL,7,Ftime tuition fees have been raised
OL,8,Fsince 2017, ITV News' Political
OL,9,FCorrespondent Harry Horton reports
OL,11,FUniversity tuition fees are set to
OL,12,Frise in England by #285 for the first
OL,13,Ftime in eight years to "secure the
OL,14,Ffuture of higher education," the
OL,15,Fgovernment has announced.
OL,17,FThe university fee cap will now be
OL,18,F#9,535 from April 2025, Education
OL,19,FSecretary Bridget Phillipson said on
OL,20,FMonday.
