OL,6,FThe maximum maintenance loan will also
OL,7,Fbe raised by #414 per year, starting
OL,8,Fin the 2025/26 academic year.
OL,10,FShe added that a lower fee limit of
OL,11,F#5,760 will be introduced for
OL,12,Ffoundation degrees.
OL,14,FSpeaking in the Commons, Phillipson
OL,15,Fsaid: "Increasing the fee cap has not
OL,16,Fbeen an easy decision, but I want to
OL,17,Fbe crystal clear that this will not
OL,18,Fcost graduates more each month as they
OL,19,Fstart to repay their loans.
