OL,3,CUniversity tuition fees set to rise by
OL,4,C#285 for first time in eight years
OL,6,FUUK chief executive Vivienne Stern
OL,7,Fsaid: "Thriving universities are
OL,8,Fessential to a thriving UK...
OL,9,FUniversity leaders and government must
OL,10,Fwork together to ensure that our
OL,11,Funiversities are able to fire on all
OL,12,Fcylinders.
OL,14,F"A decade-long freeze in England has
OL,15,Fseen inflation erode the real value of
OL,16,Fstudent fees and maintenance loans by
OL,17,Faround a third, which is completely
OL,18,Funsustainable for both students and
OL,19,Funiversities. Keeping pace with
OL,20,Finflation stops the value of fees
OL,21,Fgoing down year after year.
